      <h2>Santa as a Service</h2>

      <p>A platform to make exchanging christmas gifts more exciting and fun.</p>

      <div class="additional">
        <p><a href="https://hemligtomte.se" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hemlig Tomte</a> ("Secret Santa" in Swedish), a simple tool for creating a Secret Santa gift exchange with your family, friends, neighbors, colleagues or anyone you want to celebrate Christmas with.</p>

        <h3>Here’s how it works</h3>
        <p>A Secret Santa gift exchange is done by a group of people where everyone is randomly assigned to become someones Secret Santa.</p>

        <ol>
          <li>Someone sets up a Secret Santa group, chooses a deadline and invites others to join.</li>
          <li>Participants decide if they want to take part and must join before the deadline. If they do, their names are added to the Secret Santa pool.</li>
          <li>On deadline day, we randomly assign everyone a Secret Santa, and send them e-mails with instructions.</li>
          <li>Everyone exchanges gifts, either in person or by mail. Good times are had by all.</li>
        </ol>

        <p><a href="https://hemligtomte.se" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Try it here!</a> (In Swedish only…)</p>
